</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/b7b4d6de89b52c5a5e6e1583cb63eaee263e307b" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:3.214ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \nabla f}"></span>. The <a href="/wiki/Nabla_symbol" title="Nabla symbol">nabla symbol</a> <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \nabla }">
