  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/1b3d363e5847bda190156e986d6a85b19c24588e" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -6.171ex; width:20.443ex; height:13.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \nabla f(p)={\begin{bmatrix}{\frac {\partial f}{\partial x_{1}}}(p)\\\vdots \\{\frac {\partial f}{\partial x_{n}}}(p)\end{bmatrix}};}"></span>
<span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math display="block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle df_{p}={\begin{bmatrix}{\frac {\partial f}{\partial x_{1}}}(p)&amp;\cdots &amp;{\frac {\partial f}{\partial x_{n}}}(p)\end{bmatrix}}.}">
